From 57d45938c293e4864f828bb2a449035e1e554a6b Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Quake3e-subtick <patches@quake3e-subtick.local>
Date: Tue, 3 Mar 2026 22:09:28 +0000
Subject: [PATCH 1/5] ftwgl: base server infrastructure

Includes USE_MV (multiview), USE_AUTH (authentication), USE_SERVER_DEMO,
structural API changes from the ftwgl fork, plus subtick changes for
sv_gameHz, frame loop, Pmove, extrapolation, antilag, and antiwarp.

Co-authored-by: Copilot <223556219+Copilot@users.noreply.github.com>
